sub_title: Post doc at Biochemistry and Cell Biology Dep., Utrecht University
summary: My professional experience so far allowed me to develop organisational skills, expertise in several techniques and flexibility in applying different protocols. I have developed the ability to work in a team and on my own, discussing results and designing experimental strategies whenever appropriate. I interact closely with scientists of different backgrounds and I have had the opportunity to train both undergraduate and graduate students. I have good oral and written communication skills, as developed through regular presentations and scientific reports to both industrial partners of the project and to the academic community. I am willing to take new professional challenges.
